133        public static BigInteger build(PumpFeatureType ...types) {
134            BigInteger ret = BigInteger.ZERO;

142        public static Set<PumpFeatureType> fromBitmask(BigInteger intMap) {

144            for (PumpFeatureType type : PumpFeatureType.values()) {
